# Phase One Visuals — Universal Context Pipeline
## Auto-runs Every Session

## ON EVERY SESSION START (Auto-Execute):
1. **Load last context** → Check `obsidian-vault/workflow-logs/` for most recent session log
2. **Read it** → Understand what was last worked on
3. **Run**: `node automation/load-context.js` → Loads OpenBrain memory + Graphify state
4. **Graphify refresh** → Run `/graphify . --update` to sync any code changes into the knowledge graph

## ON EVERY SESSION END (Manual / Auto):
Run this command to save everything:
```
node automation/save-context.js
```
This will:
- ✓ Save session log to `obsidian-vault/workflow-logs/`
- ✓ Write findings to OpenBrain
- ✓ Commit + push to GitHub (so next chat anywhere can pull context)
- ✓ Print a full summary of what was done

## Cross-Chat Context Sharing
Since the vault is **git-pushed to GitHub**, any chat with access to this repo can:
```
git pull
node automation/load-context.js
```
And get full context — works across Copilot, Claude, Cursor, any IDE.

## Quick Commands
| Action | Command |
|--------|---------|
| Save all context | `node automation/save-context.js` |
| Load all context | `node automation/load-context.js` |
| Build graph | `/graphify .` |
| Update graph | `/graphify . --update` |
| Query graph | `/graphify query "<question>"` |

## How It Works
```
┌─────────────────┐     ┌───────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────┐
│  Any Chat/IDE   │────▶│  automation/      │────▶│  GitHub Repo    │
│  (Copilot, etc) │     │  save-context.js  │     │  (Central Hub)  │
└─────────────────┘     └───────────────────┘     └─────────────────┘
        │                                                     │
        │                                                     │
        ▼                                                     ▼
┌─────────────────┐                                   ┌─────────────────┐
│  obsidian-vault │◀──────────────────────────────────▶│  Next Chat Anywhere
│  + OpenBrain    │    git push / git pull             │  gets full context
└─────────────────┘                                   └─────────────────┘